			<node ID="ID_1018949062" TEXT="As the name suggests the Global Descriptor Table is an array of descriptors available to specify and define system wide resources (hence describe those resources).. More often than not the resource is an area of continuous memory but there are other kinds of very important resources too.. The taxonomy of the descriptors is. Descriptors Non system descriptors Code segment descriptor Data " />
