			<node ID="ID_271828115" TEXT="When the processor is in virtual-8086 mode the CPL is 3. Therefore an 8086 processor program has only user privileges. If the pages of the virtual-8086 monitor have supervisor privilege they cannot be accessed by the 8086 program. 20.2.5 Entering Virtual-8086 Mode. Figure 20-3 summarizes the methods of entering and leaving" />
			</node>
