			<node ID="ID_416077099" TEXT="15.3 Entering and Leaving V86 Mode Figure 15-2 summarizes the ways that the processor can enter and leave an 8086 program. The processor can enter V86 by either of two means: A task switch to an 80386 task loads the image of EFLAGS from the new TSS." />
